com.example.bookflow.Model

Class Book

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.bookflow.Model.Book

  • public class Book
extends java.lang.Object
    The book model class. It contains information about a book, including title, author of the book, ISBN number, photoURI, description and book info. It also contains book status information including current status, ownerID and borrower ID.
